.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the start position to use
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player/start_position.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the starting location of the player.  This the
location they will start at if the saved position does not work
for some reason.
.EP

